{"tid":2214912,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【蘋果日報英文版...】有時好驚香港報紙社評講國際事務","createTime":"2020-09-23T14:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T01:05:50.000Z","uid":138409,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d8d7a2b0ce2b3a28c736db6cc7c56a4e141731","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:53:08.000Z","msg":"來源：歐洲動態fb<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/photos/a.566872090026410/3304410009605924\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Feuropechinese%2Fphotos%2Fa.566872090026410%2F3304410009605924&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=0af7de7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/europechinese/photos/a.566872090026410/3304410009605924</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/119893666_3304410016272590_6398655711445875729_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=5xxW48dRrGEAX-negov&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-1.xx&amp;oh=aed8eb8131b24021d15a6f0c4e346c3a&amp;oe=5F90BC0E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F119893666_3304410016272590_6398655711445875729_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3D5xxW48dRrGEAX-negov%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-1.xx%26oh%3Daed8eb8131b24021d15a6f0c4e346c3a%26oe%3D5F90BC0E&h=8a044f13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時好驚香港報紙社評講國際事務，例如有社評將RBG對憲法/法例解釋嘅理論、方法形容為「法官干政」，解釋為「人們貪方便走捷徑，將原應循折衝妥協政治解決的眾人之事訴諸法庭，交法官裁決」，又話RBG等傾向呢個詮釋法例態度嘅法官為「權力人之所欲也，法官亦不例外。抗拒權力引誘、守誡自持，談何容易」，成件事膚淺到恐怖嘅地步。<br />\n<br />\n美國最高法院點審案，一向有爭議，但呢個係涉及點樣解釋憲法，以及司法一權喺美國三權之中扮演乜嘢角色。最簡單就係，究竟憲法應該盡量以字面去解釋VS以更廣闊嘅角度去解釋憲法&mdash;&mdash;呢個講法已經係高度簡化，前者都唔代表剩係「照字面解」，因為咁樣係一定解唔到一部二百幾年前訂立嘅憲法，而後者亦唔係亂Q咁解，都要有一套理論去解釋點解可以咁樣解法。<br />\n<br />\n而點樣解釋部憲法，美國有好多唔同「乜乜ism」嘅理論。<span class=\"gold\">美國就算最反對RBG審案方法嘅人，都係有返個堆「乜乜ism」去解釋點解咁樣解法有問題，而唔會超級簡化到一句「法官干政」咁簡單。</span><br />\n<br />\n而且成篇社評&mdash;&mdash;以及好多我睇過唔少中國人、例如旅美中國人&mdash;&mdash;嘅睇法，都係<span class=\"gold\">抽空咗美國政治同歷史嘅脈絡去評論</span>，無視美國司法一權喺政治嘅地位，同大部份其他西方民主國家係好唔同，呢個涉及美國自己獨有嘅歷史同政治秩序，唔可以簡單將英國或其他國家嘅一套套入去美國。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">呢啲去脈絡化嘅國際事時評論，放喺香港媒體，對象喺香港人嘅話，只會誤導香港受眾，無助香港人加深了解國際事務，反而令香港人對國際事務睇法變得膚淺。</span><br />\n<br />\n呢篇社評亦有譯做英文，放喺同一媒體嘅英語平台，據聞呢個平台係「打國際線」，想外國人有更多途徑去了解香港目前嘅人權民主自由狀況，但呢啲咁嘅社評畀外國人睇到，只會覺得香港爭取自由民主嘅運動同美國共和黨/保守派/侵侵綑綁。我唔太sure支持美國保守派(仲要喺頗極端嘅一翼)，喺國際間有幾多fans。如果國際線係咁打嘅話，真係唔打好過打。"},{"pid":"a6be2846f0c1ca4f14b11dab7dd830aa07619d82","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0de1330f6624d73d8ef417b0fef0013d1bd40a","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"46005a7b8fb67493e393180f17e04489356ecf64","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:57:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ffc0b3324dd6aea5af60df940dc54261eac86f64","tid":2214912,"uid":134247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"屈鳩RBG濫權<br />\n戇撚鳩"},{"pid":"16b58f2d2195002a3c281adf941cd1487ce5e076","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:58:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4a8307cbe2edf1511817457f36774ec4a4874295","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffc0b3324dd6aea5af60df940dc54261eac86f64","tid":2214912,"uid":134247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"屈鳩RBG濫權<br />\n戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她在擔任大法官時期，也常運用具有保守特徵的方式論理，例如，她對於程序的重視、對於聯邦主義原則的堅持，或者強調限縮司法權，這些原則都彰顯了保守派的特徵。也或許是金斯堡對於保守原則的尊重，使得大法官們在彼此面對不同意見時，都能維持相互尊重與理解。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=5749dafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media 版權所有 翻印必究"},{"pid":"4de2b6e740191dfee79192e2d75aa7bc8928b811","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a8307cbe2edf1511817457f36774ec4a4874295","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffc0b3324dd6aea5af60df940dc54261eac86f64","tid":2214912,"uid":134247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"屈鳩RBG濫權<br />\n戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她在擔任大法官時期，也常運用具有保守特徵的方式論理，例如，她對於程序的重視、對於聯邦主義原則的堅持，或者強調限縮司法權，這些原則都彰顯了保守派的特徵。也或許是金斯堡對於保守原則的尊重，使得大法官們在彼此面對不同意見時，都能維持相互尊重與理解。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=5749dafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media 版權所有 翻印必究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:02:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/CFEHVD35IRBY5MB3HPN64ALKSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FCFEHVD35IRBY5MB3HPN64ALKSI%2F&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=1dfdb385\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200923%2FCFEHVD35IRBY5MB3HPN64ALKSI%2F&h=a495349e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200923/CFEHVD35IRBY5MB3HPN64ALKSI/</a><br />\n// 在今天的香港，要評論像金斯伯格這樣的一名開明派偶像人物，未免有點困難。畢竟，開明派往往會被視為離地萬丈的理想主義者，然後一大堆「左膠」帽子扣下來。然而，真正熟悉美國政治的評論者會知道金斯伯格恐怕是最「左而不膠」的代表。<span class=\"gold\">她的名言「為你介懷的事情奮鬥，但要用能引領別人追隨你的方式」，正正指出從政者不應只顧自我感覺良好，在今天的香港無論泛民本土均值得學習。</span>//"},{"pid":"05419ea379326d8cb85f397871283d5899107934","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:03:03.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"774ef542e1527856d412aa45dd6599b625d784ca","tid":2214912,"uid":134247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a8307cbe2edf1511817457f36774ec4a4874295","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffc0b3324dd6aea5af60df940dc54261eac86f64","tid":2214912,"uid":134247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"屈鳩RBG濫權<br />\n戇撚鳩"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:00:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>她在擔任大法官時期，也常運用具有保守特徵的方式論理，例如，她對於程序的重視、對於聯邦主義原則的堅持，或者強調限縮司法權，這些原則都彰顯了保守派的特徵。也或許是金斯堡對於保守原則的尊重，使得大法官們在彼此面對不同意見時，都能維持相互尊重與理解。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law/?utm_medium=copy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftheinitium.com%2Farticle%2F20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law%2F%3Futm_medium%3Dcopy&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9gx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=5749dafa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://theinitium.com/article/20200922-opinion-rgb-feminism-law/?utm_medium=copy</a> <br />\n&copy; 端傳媒 Initium Media 版權所有 翻印必究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:03:33.000Z","msg":"大權同濫權都可以撈埋呢講<br />\n端呢篇唔錯，fair comment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e1ac1f5dbbc21a7bf1535f112aa08c39a8bc7c","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dc8cb3d61cd6266e30da31c4a19a0586e3950a8d","tid":2214912,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":